er winter in the 2023/2024 season has hung over Vail</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/627909228/image_627909228.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743664-vail-resorts-the-clouds-are-lifting", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 22:24:11"}, {"id": "4743663", "title": "Chimerix: Big News, Big Moves, So Maybe Now's The Time To Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/74180173/image_74180173.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Wooden staircase and handrail\" data-id=\"74180173\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1008px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/74180173/image_74180173.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/74180173/image_74180173.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/74180173/image_74180173.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/74180173/image_74180173.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/74180173/image_74180173.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/74180173/image_74180173.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/74180173/image_74180173.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/74180173/image_74180173.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Tom Merton/OJO Images via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Topline Summary and Update</h2> <p>When I first took a look at <b>Chimerix, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CMRX\" title=\"Chimerix, Inc.\">CMRX</a></span>) <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CMRX/analysis#:~:text=Chimerix%3A%20Tackling%20A%20Strong%20Unmet%20Need%20With%20Promising%20Data\">back in March 2024</a>, I expressed substantial optimism for the investment thesis at the price the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/74180173/image_74180173.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743663-chimerix-big-news-big-moves-so-maybe-now-time-to-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 22:19:24"}, {"id": "4743659", "title": "GSK Is Doing The Right Things But Can't Catch A Break - Rating Downgrade", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448400357/image_1448400357.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Serious Businesswoman Driving Car\" data-id=\"1448400357\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448400357/image_1448400357.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448400357/image_1448400357.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448400357/image_1448400357.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448400357/image_1448400357.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448400357/image_1448400357.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448400357/image_1448400357.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448400357/image_1448400357.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448400357/image_1448400357.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">miniseries/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Overview</h2> <p>I made the stock of <b>GSK plc</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GSK\" title=\"GSK plc\">GSK</a></span>), the United Kingdom-based Pharma giant and the fourteenth most valuable Pharma in the US and Europe by market cap\u2014currently ~$72bn\u2014a buy after </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1448400357/image_1448400357.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743659-gsk-is-doing-the-right-things-but-cant-catch-a-break-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 22:08:00"}, {"id": "4743656", "title": "SWBI: Time To Double Down On Guns", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956210960/image_956210960.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Rodeo Competition\" data-id=\"956210960\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956210960/image_956210960.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956210960/image_956210960.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956210960/image_956210960.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956210960/image_956210960.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956210960/image_956210960.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_image