: Under The Radar Roll-Up With Attractive Unit Economics", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2175923913/image_2175923913.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Sunset over the Racetrack\" data-id=\"2175923913\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2175923913/image_2175923913.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2175923913/image_2175923913.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2175923913/image_2175923913.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2175923913/image_2175923913.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2175923913/image_2175923913.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2175923913/image_2175923913.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2175923913/image_2175923913.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2175923913/image_2175923913.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">ReDunnLev/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p>WillScot Holdings Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/WSC\" title=\"WillScot Holdings Corporation\">WSC</a></span>) is an interesting opportunity at current prices as the company works through some shareholder turnover following the FTC's decision to shoot down its pending merger with McGrath RentCorp</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2175923913/image_2175923913.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743651-willscot-holdings-under-the-radar-rollup-with-attractive-unit-economics", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 21:47:58"}, {"id": "4743648", "title": "OraSure Technologies: Discounted Assets With An Attractive Free Call Option", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1310164207/image_1310164207.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Rapid test for infectious disease in open mouth.\" data-id=\"1310164207\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1310164207/image_1310164207.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1310164207/image_1310164207.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1310164207/image_1310164207.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1310164207/image_1310164207.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1310164207/image_1310164207.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1310164207/image_1310164207.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1310164207/image_1310164207.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1310164207/image_1310164207.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Guido Mieth/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Summary</strong></h2> <p>Based in Pennsylvania, OraSure Technologies, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OSUR\" title=\"OraSure Technologies, Inc.\">OSUR</a></span>) is a small-cap diagnostics company with a long track record as a public company, having gone public in November 1986. Despite its long public history and its</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1310164207/image_1310164207.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743648-orasure-technologies-discounted-assets-with-an-attractive-free-call-option", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 21:34:44"}, {"id": "4743662", "title": "Trump And China Add To Copper Headwinds In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1418196145/image_1418196145.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Background of Copper , digital photo image\" data-id=\"1418196145\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1017px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1418196145/image_1418196145.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1418196145/image_1418196145.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1418196145/image_1418196145.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1418196145/image_1418196145.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1418196145/image_1418196145.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1418196145/image_1418196145.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1418196145/image_1418196145.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn